text: Loes Adegeest (born 7 August 1996) is a Dutch racing cyclist and speed skater. As a cyclist she currently rides for Dutch amateur team Jan van Arckel, after riding for Parkhotel Valkenburg. ==References== ==External links== * * Profile at speedskatingnews Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female cyclists Category:Dutch female speed skaters Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
